~ shorter alexadd in mouse.

&TIME &SEED               ~ painfully obvious

? ?                       ~ get some input
&RAND 10 * &INT 8 >       ~ get a random number 0-1 * 10, make it an int & check if >8
[                         ~ if true
  + 1 + !                 ~ add the input then add 1 and print
|                         ~ else
  + !                     ~ add and print
]                         ~ endif

~ Golfed:
~ &TIME &SEED ?? &RAND 10* &INT 8>[+1+!|+!]
